    public interface ActionBuilder
extends Function<BiSupplier<Action,​BiConsumer<EObject,​Action>>,​Action>
    Adapter interface. Builds an action for the target. Implementations shall call the argument BiConsumer passing the target and resulting action as argument to use later in resolve() phase.
